slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"咪話咗之前果啲人錯哂嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cd7a4d3c8a0dc6fb1ddc65c668b813c40a3fb6","tid":2183530,"uid":365024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"<ins>FACV 1/2014</ins><br />\n<em><strong><span class=\"small\">Leung Kwok Hung v. President of the Legislative Council of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region</span></strong><br />\n</em><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><blockquote>(4)   The appeal raised two questions of constitutional law described in paragraph 2 of the Court&rsquo;s Reasons for Judgment as being of &ldquo;fundamental importance&rdquo; relating to the doctrine of the separation of powers under the Basic Law.  It follows that the appeal is properly to be characterised as having been brought with a view to obtaining guidance on a point of general public importance for the benefit of the community as a whole.<br />\n<br />\n&bull;《基本法》條文包括三權分立的信條（doctrine），以及其中立法機關與法院之間的關係。<br />\n&bull; 這種關係包括以下原則：法院承認立法機關在處理內部事務的專有權，特別是立法過程。<br />\n&bull; 法院不會插手裁決立法機關內部程序的合規或違規事項，會留給立法機關自行決定（「不干預原則」）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=96088&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D96088%26currpage%3DT&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=c82216a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=96088&amp;currpage=T</a></blockquote></span>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6a17de78ca77b2f61bd091e402d84496efb963cc","tid":2183530,"uid":119895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nHX3rHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnHX3rHM.png&h=267a06c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下邊個係代表政府既大狀？"}}